    <item>
      <title><![CDATA[Data URIs 小试]]></title>
      <link>http://keyfoxth.github.io/2015/10/13/data-uris/</link>
      <guid>http://keyfoxth.github.io/2015/10/13/data-uris/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Oct 2015 15:42:39 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      <![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>15-10-26 第 4 次更新</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h3 id="简介">简介</h3><p>data URIs 由 <a href="http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2397">RFC 2397</a> 定义，允许将一个小文件进行编码后嵌入到另外一个文档里。</p>
<p>注意：是 <code>URI</code> 而不是 <code>URL</code>，<code>URL</code>（Universal Resource Locator，统一资源定位符）是 <code>URI</code>（Universal Resource Identifier，统一资源标识符）的子集。</p>
<h3 id="语法结构">语法结构</h3><pre><code>data:[<span class="link_label">&lt;media type&gt;</span>][<span class="link_reference">;charset=&lt;character set&gt;</span>][<span class="link_label">;base64</span>],<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">data</span>&gt;</span></span>
</code></pre><ol>
<li><code>data:</code> 协议头，标识这是一个 data URI 资源。</li>
<li><code>[&lt;media type&gt;]</code> 数据呈现的格式，例如 <code>image/gif</code> 代表 gif 图像文件，如果没有指定，默认是 <code>text/plain</code>。</li>
<li><code>[;charset=&lt;character set&gt;]</code> 可选的字符集参数，如果没有指定，默认是 <code>US-ASCII</code>。</li>
<li><code>[;base64]</code> 可选的数据编码方式，存在时，表示 <code>&lt;data&gt;</code> 是 base64 编码过的二进制数据。</li>
<li><code>&lt;data&gt;</code> 实际的数据内容，八比特的字符序列。</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="用法">用法</h3><p>在 HTML 中：</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">img</span> <span class="attribute">src</span>=<span class="value">"data:image/gif;base64,XXXXX"</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在 CSS 中：</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">div</span> <span class="rules">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="rule"><span class="attribute">background-image</span>:<span class="value"> <span class="function">url</span>(<span class="string">"data:image/gif;base64,XXXXX"</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在 JavaScript 中：</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">window</span>.open(<span class="string">"data:text/html;charset=utf-8,"</span> +</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">encodeURIComponent</span>(</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;"</span>+</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"&lt;html lang="</span>zh-CN<span class="string">"&gt;"</span>+</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"&lt;head&gt;&lt;title&gt;Hello, world!&lt;/title&gt;&lt;/head&gt;"</span>+</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"&lt;body&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Hello, world!&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;/body&gt;"</span>+</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"&lt;/html&gt;"</span></span><br><span class="line">  )</span><br><span class="line">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]>
      
      </description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>15-10-26 第 4 次更新</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h3 id="简介">简介</h3><p>data URIs 由 <a href="http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2397" target="_blank" rel="external">RFC 2397</a> 定义，允许将一个小文件进行编码后嵌入到另外一个文档里。</p>
<p>注意：是 <code>URI</code> 而不是 <code>URL</code>，<code>URL</code>（Universal Resource Locator，统一资源定位符）是 <code>URI</code>（Universal Resource Identifier，统一资源标识符）的子集。</p>
<h3 id="语法结构">语法结构</h3><pre><code>data:[<span class="link_label">&lt;media type&gt;</span>][<span class="link_reference">;charset=&lt;character set&gt;</span>][<span class="link_label">;base64</span>],<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">data</span>&gt;</span></span>
</code></pre><ol>
<li><code>data:</code> 协议头，标识这是一个 data URI 资源。</li>
<li><code>[&lt;media type&gt;]</code> 数据呈现的格式，例如 <code>image/gif</code> 代表 gif 图像文件，如果没有指定，默认是 <code>text/plain</code>。</li>
<li><code>[;charset=&lt;character set&gt;]</code> 可选的字符集参数，如果没有指定，默认是 <code>US-ASCII</code>。</li>
<li><code>[;base64]</code> 可选的数据编码方式，存在时，表示 <code>&lt;data&gt;</code> 是 base64 编码过的二进制数据。</li>
<li><code>&lt;data&gt;</code> 实际的数据内容，八比特的字符序列。</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="用法">用法</h3><p>在 HTML 中：</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">img</span> <span class="attribute">src</span>=<span class="value">"data:image/gif;base64,XXXXX"</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在 CSS 中：</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">div</span> <span class="rules">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="rule"><span class="attribute">background-image</span>:<span class="value"> <span class="function">url</span>(<span class="string">"data:image/gif;base64,XXXXX"</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在 JavaScript 中：</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">window</span>.open(<span class="string">"data:text/html;charset=utf-8,"</span> +</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">encodeURIComponent</span>(</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;"</span>+</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"&lt;html lang="</span>zh-CN<span class="string">"&gt;"</span>+</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"&lt;head&gt;&lt;title&gt;Hello, world!&lt;/title&gt;&lt;/head&gt;"</span>+</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"&lt;body&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Hello, world!&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;/body&gt;"</span>+</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"&lt;/html&gt;"</span></span><br><span class="line">  )</span><br><span class="line">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<a id="more"></a>
<h3 id="实例">实例</h3><p><a href="data:text/html;charset=UTF-8,Hello, world!" target="_blank" rel="external">DEMO</a> <a href=""></a></p>
<p><img src="data:image/gif;base64,"></p>
<p>当然，Data URIs 的使用情景更多的是嵌入图片，以下的优缺点描述的也是在嵌入图片时的情形。</p>
<h3 id="优点">优点</h3><ol>
<li>最重要的优点：节省 HTTP Requests。这是除了纯粹的文档大小之外，最影响网页加载速度的因素。</li>
<li>将 Data URIs 写在 HTML 里，可以避免在更换图片后，缓存的清理问题。</li>
<li>将 Data URIs 写在 CSS、JavaScript，可以依靠缓存 CSS、JavaScript 文件来缓存 Data URIs。</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="缺点">缺点</h3>]]></content:encoded>
